TopicTitle: Launching 1.1 crashes Linux Mint Cinnamon to backup mode

Articles.Content:
1.1.0.1230 crashes my LinuxMint Cinnamon desktop on open. Reproduced after full reboot. If Cinnamon is not allowed to go into backup mode the game appears playable, otherwise it's just a black screen. I have the logs from the second occurrence when I prevented Cinnamon from going to backup.
